snippet.title: १ किलो भाजणीची चकली बनवताना या १० चुका टाळा | चकली जिभेवर विरघळणार तेलात नाही | 1 Kilo Bhajni Chakli
snippet.description:
Please take a moment to like and subscribe ✿◕ ‿ ◕✿
https://www.youtube.com/@MadhurasRecipeMarathi

मधुराज् रेसिपीचे नवीन पुस्तक खरेदी करण्यासाठी खाली दिलेल्या लिंक वर क्लिक करा. 
स्वयंपाक घरातील तंत्र आणि मंत्र - https://amzn.to/45aHlGW
डायबेटीस फ्रेंडली आहार नियोजन - मराठी - https://amzn.to/43QlLpK
Diabetes Friendly Meal Planning - English - https://amzn.to/453miWo

दिवाळी फराळ विशेष भाजणीची चकली बनवण्यासाठी लागणारे साहित्य 
भाजणी 
• २ १/२ / ५०० ग्रॅम तांदूळ 
• १ कप / २०० ग्रॅम चणाडाळ 
• १/२ कप / १०० ग्रॅम मुगडाळ 
• १/२ कप / १०० ग्रॅम उडीद डाळ 
• १/२ कप / १०० ग्रॅम पोहे 
• २० ग्रॅम धने 
• २० ग्रॅम जिरं 
चकली 
• ३ कप पाणी 
• १/४ कप तेल 
• १ चमचा लाल तिखट 
• चवीनुसार मीठ 
• १ मोठा चमचा धनेपूड 
• १ किलो चकली भाजणी 
• १ चमचा ओवा 
• १ चमचा पांढरे तीळ 
• तळण्यासाठी तेल

मधुराज रेसिपीचं इतर पुस्तक खरेदी करण्यासाठी खालील लिंकवर क्लिक करा. 
मराठी - आहार नियोजन - https://amzn.to/3HwQmkh
90 Days Meal Planning - https://amzn.to/406MdLe

Follow MadhurasRecipe for more such yummy and delicious recipes
Subscribe MadhurasRecipe Marathi - https://ggle.io/3QOx
Subscribe MadhurasRecipe Hindi - https://ggle.io/3QOz
Subscribe MadhurasRecipe - https://ggle.io/3QP1
Like Facebook - https://fbook.cc/3FNz
Join Facebook group - https://fbook.cc/3GAo
Follow Instagram - https://fbook.cc/3FO0
https://twitter.com/madhurasrecipe
Website - http://www.madhurasrecipe.com

#chakalirecipe #madhurasrecipe #bhajnichakli

Ingredients:
Bhajani
• 2 1/2 cup / 500 gm Rice
• 1 cup / 200 gm Chana dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Moong dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Urad dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Poha
• 20 gm Coriander seeds
• 20 gm Cumin seeds
Chakali
• 3 cups Water
• 1/4 cup Oil
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• Salt to taste
• 1 tbsp Coriander powder
• 1 kilo Chakali bhajani
• 1 tsp Ajwain / Carom seeds
• 1 tsp white Sesame seeds
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Wipe the rice really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe chana dal really good with clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe moong dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe urad dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• You can wash and dry all these ingredients if you want. 
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and roast rice really good. 
• The rice should be roasted well but the color should not change. 
• When the rice is roasted well take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast chana dal really good until it begins to get reddish color and take it out into 
  a dish. 
• In the same pan roast moong dal well until it gets reddish color and take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast urad dal really good until it gets light golden color and take it out into a 
  dish. 
• Roast poha really good and transfer them into the dish. 
• In the same pan roast coriander seeds and cumin seeds together on low heat until nice aroma 
  begins to release from it and transfer it into the dish. 
• Mix everything well together and let it cool down. 
• Grind it from the mill. Make sure that it is ground after rice or jawar is ground and not after wheat. 
• Blend it into flour in mixer and sieve it through flour strainer. 
• Blend the leftover coarse flour in the strain again in blender and sieve it. Bhajani for chakali is 
  ready.
Chakali
• Heat up water in a pan and add oil. 
• Mix well and add red chili powder, salt, coriander powder. 
• Mix well and when the mixture boils really good, reduce the heat to low. 
• Add the bhajani flour and turn off the gas. 
• Add carom seeds, sesame seeds and mix everything well together quickly. 
• Transfer the ukad into a dish and knead dough. If needed use very little hot water. 
• Knead the ukad really good when it is still hot. The consistency of the dough should be stiff. 
• Take small portion from the dough and knead it really good again. 
• Make a smooth and even roll and transfer it into chakali machine. 
• Press the dough well and roll out chakali from it on a butter paper. 
• Seal both the ends of the chakali really good. 
•You can use plastic sheet or dish in place of butter paper. 
• Heat up oil in a pan on medium to high heat for about 6-7 minutes and drop a small chakali in it. 
• If it is fried well, then the oil is hot enough. 
• Drop chakali into hot oil and fry well. 
• When the chakali begins to settle at the bottom, flip it over and fry well from other side too. 
• When chakali begins to settle at the bottom of the pan, it means it is fried well from both sides. 
• Take the chakali out, drain excess oil and transfer it into a dish. Chakali is ready.

Ingredients:
Bhajani
• 2 1/2 cup / 500 gm Rice
• 1 cup / 200 gm Chana dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Moong dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Urad dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Poha
• 20 gm Coriander seeds
• 20 gm Cumin seeds
Chakali
• 3 cups Water
• 1/4 cup Oil
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• Salt to taste
• 1 tbsp Coriander powder
• 1 kilo Chakali bhajani
• 1 tsp Ajwain / Carom seeds
• 1 tsp white Sesame seeds
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Wipe the rice really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe chana dal really good with clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe moong dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe urad dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• You can wash and dry all these ingredients if you want. 
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and roast rice really good. 
• The rice should be roasted well but the color should not change. 
• When the rice is roasted well take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast chana dal really good until it begins to get reddish color and take it out into 
  a dish. 
• In the same pan roast moong dal well until it gets reddish color and take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast urad dal really good until it gets light golden color and take it out into a 
  dish. 
• Roast poha really good and transfer them into the dish. 
• In the same pan roast coriander seeds and cumin seeds together on low heat until nice aroma 
  begins to release from it and transfer it into the dish. 
• Mix everything well together and let it cool down. 
• Grind it from the mill. Make sure that it is ground after rice or jawar is ground and not after wheat. 
• Blend it into flour in mixer and sieve it through flour strainer. 
• Blend the leftover coarse flour in the strain again in blender and sieve it. Bhajani for chakali is 
  ready.
Chakali
• Heat up water in a pan and add oil. 
• Mix well and add red chili powder, salt, coriander powder. 
• Mix well and when the mixture boils really good, reduce the heat to low. 
• Add the bhajani flour and turn off the gas. 
• Add carom seeds, sesame seeds and mix everything well together quickly. 
• Transfer the ukad into a dish and knead dough. If needed use very little hot water. 
• Knead the ukad really good when it is still hot. The consistency of the dough should be stiff. 
• Take small portion from the dough and knead it really good again. 
• Make a smooth and even roll and transfer it into chakali machine. 
• Press the dough well and roll out chakali from it on a butter paper. 
• Seal both the ends of the chakali really good. 
•You can use plastic sheet or dish in place of butter paper. 
• Heat up oil in a pan on medium to high heat for about 6-7 minutes and drop a small chakali in it. 
• If it is fried well, then the oil is hot enough. 
• Drop chakali into hot oil and fry well. 
• When the chakali begins to settle at the bottom, flip it over and fry well from other side too. 
• When chakali begins to settle at the bottom of the pan, it means it is fried well from both sides. 
• Take the chakali out, drain excess oil and transfer it into a dish. Chakali is ready.

Lyrics:-
Rakka Rakka 

Female:
Oh manikuruvi 
Mehalkuruvi
Man ki rani…

En manimaaran 
Magadeeran 
Raajavaaroo

Rajakulathin 
Kodiparakkum
Malvaatheril 

Noorazhakodi-
Nnavan enne 
Kaanan vanno 

Male:
Nee madhura punchirikaari 
Enn maayavaani 
Yavana sundhari tholkkum 
Enn vaazhvin devi 

Vala thilangana kayyil 
Kayycherthe ninne 
Vara sumangaliaaki 
Njan konde pokum 

Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa

Female:
Aanveeran thottal pookum 
Aaromal Pennaanenne 
Mevaarin aramanayum njanum 
Ninn swantham…

(Rakka Rakka)

Female:
Raavirullunnu…
Vazhipaatha mangunnu…
Ivale kavaraan aararum 
Vannaalo…

Male:
Ethu sulthaanum 
Padakootti vannotte …
Udalvaalthala than 
Choodaale ninne njan 
Kaakkoole…

Female:
Nenjillu nenjillu neeyalle 
Mundhiya munthiri thenalle 
Ennile ennilu vannaal njan 
Veenjaay thoovaam…

Male:
Ponmani kothiya pallakkil 
Munnilananja nilaavalle 
Kallupathichoru koolaarin 
Ponnalle 

Kannalle…

Chorus:
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa

Female:
Kannaalan kayyaal thottaal 
Poopookkum 
Pennaanenne…

Mevaarin aramanayum njanum 
Ninn swantham…

(Rakka Rakka)

snippet.title: Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Director Wes Ball breathes new life into the global, epic franchise set several generations in the future following Caesar’s reign, in which apes are the dominant species living harmoniously and humans have been reduced to living in the shadows. As a new tyrannical ape leader builds his empire, one young ape undertakes a harrowing journey that will cause him to question all that he has known about the past and to make choices that will define a future for apes and humans alike.

“Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes” is directed by Wes Ball (the “Maze Runner” trilogy) and stars Owen Teague (“IT”), Freya Allan (“The Witcher”), Kevin Durand (Locke & Key”), Peter Macon (“Shameless”), and William H. Macy (“Fargo”). The screenplay is by Josh Friedman (“War of the Worlds”) and Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver (“Avatar: The Way of Water”) and Patrick Aison (“Prey”), based on characters created by Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and the producers are Wes Ball, Joe Hartwick, Jr. (“The Maze Runner”), Rick Jaffa, Amanda Silver, Jason Reed (“Mulan”), with Peter Chernin (the “Planet of the Apes” trilogy) and Jenno Topping (“Ford v. Ferrari”) serving as executive producers.

snippet.title: Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha | Part 1
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, envisioning #Vijay in the LCU, and more 

This is the first part of the interaction.   #CinemaExpress 

00:10 - 01:45  - Loki and The Kerala Story
01:46 - 02:45 - How did Loki respond to the polarising responses 
02:46 - 04:40 - How did Loki accept the criticism about the flashback
04:41 - 08.40 - How Loki fixed the duration of Leo
08:41 - 09:40 - What does Loki believe is the truth of Leo?  
09:41 - 10:54  - What is Loki's favourite thing about the Leo flashback
10:55 - 12:00 - Is Loki really constrained by fans 
12:01 - 16:16 - What does it take for young directors like Loki to work with superstars
16:17 - 20:40 - How does Loki see the audience's fixation on box-office numbers
20:41 - 24:38 - Who does Loki think is the villain of Leo? 
24:39 - 25:43 - Loki opens about the Hulk Connect in Leo
25:44 - 28:56 - Is Leo a good person or a bad person? 
28:57 - 32.30 - Is Loki glorifying the bad guy in Leo? 
32:31 - 32:56 - What is Parthiban's take on a drug-free society? 
32:57 - 33.24 - Does Loki really think the twin angle worked in favour of the film? 
33:25 - 37:58 - How does Loki work with his writing room? 
37:59 - 42:05 - Does Loki feel the pressure of casting the big names
42:06 - 50:00 - The big question of Loki and LCU
Follow us on

Twitter: https://twitter.com/XpressCinema
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xpresscinema/

For more film news, interviews and reviews, go to: http://www.cinemaexpress.com

Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

snippet.title: The Fall Guy | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Stuntman becomes the hero. #TheFallGuyMovie only in theaters March 1.

------

He’s a stuntman, and like everyone in the stunt community, he gets blown up, shot, crashed, thrown through windows and dropped from the highest of heights, all for our entertainment. And now, fresh off an almost career-ending accident, this working-class hero has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job. What could possibly go right? 

From real life stunt man and director David Leitch, the blockbuster director of Bullet Train, Deadpool 2, Atomic Blonde and Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw and the producer of John Wick, Nobody and Violent Night, comes his most personal film yet. A new hilarious, hard-driving, all-star apex-action thriller and love letter to action movies and the hard-working and under-appreciated crew of people who make them: The Fall Guy. 

Oscar® nominee Ryan Gosling (Barbie, La La Land, Drive) stars as Colt Seavers, a battle-scarred stuntman who, having left the business a year earlier to focus on both his physical and mental health, is drafted back into service when the star of a mega-budget studio movie—being directed by his ex, Jody Moreno, played by Golden Globe winner Emily Blunt (Oppenheimer, A Quiet Place films, Sicario)—goes missing.

While the film’s ruthless producer (Emmy winner Hannah Waddingham; Ted Lasso), maneuvers to keep the disappearance of star Tom Ryder (Golden Globe winner Aaron Taylor-Johnson; Bullet Train) a secret from the studio and the media, Colt performs the film’s most outrageous stunts while trying (with limited success) to charm his way back into Jody’s good graces. But as the mystery around the missing star deepens, Colt will find himself ensnared in a sinister, criminal plot that will push him to the edge of a fall more dangerous than any stunt.

Inspired by the hit 1980s TV series, The Fall Guy also stars Winston Duke (Black Panther franchise) and Academy Award® nominee Stephanie Hsu (Everything Everywhere All at Once). 

From a screenplay by Hobbs & Shaw screenwriter Drew Pearce, The Fall Guy is produced by Kelly McCormick (Bullet Train, Nobody, Atomic Blonde) and David Leitch for their company 87North, and by Ryan Gosling and by Guymon Casady (Game of Thrones, Steve Jobs and executive producer of the upcoming series Ripley) for Entertainment 360. The film is executive produced by Drew Pearce, Entertainment 360’s Geoff Shaevitz and the creator of the original Fall Guy television series, Glen A. Larson.

Website: http://www.TheFallGuyMovie.com
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/thefallguymovie 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/thefallguymovie 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@Universalpics 
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/@UniversalPictures
X: https://twitter.com/thefallguymovie

snippet.title: PART 2 Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, bringing #Vijay into the LCU, and more 

This is the SECOND part of the interaction

00:00 - 5:22 - Including History of Violence, what are the other inspirations in Loki's films

05:23 - 07:00 - How did Loki sketch the husband-wife equation in Leo

07:01 - 09:44 - How did the hyena come into the Loki Universe

09:45 - 12:08 - What does Loki think of how people connect the hyena metaphor and other layers of Leo 

12:09 - 14:23 - What elevated Loki's cinematic knowledge

14:24 - 17:48 - What does Loki think of the audience understanding? 

17:49 - 19:37 - What are the plans for the hyena in the LCU? 

19:38 - 20:49 - Will Loki attempt the horror genre? 

20:50 - 23.58 - How does Loki zero in on the retro songs in his films? 

23:59 - 26:16 - How does Loki create an atmosphere for usage of these songs? 

26:17 - 27:20 - What inspired Loki to make that badass Vijay intro card?

27:21 - 28:11 - Why does Loki believe second time is the charm? 

28:12 - 28:38 - Loki on finally bringing Mansoor Ali Khan into the LCU

28:39 - 29:57 - What were the steps Loki took to ensure Parthiban's body adapted to the war scars?
 
29:58 - 32:16 - How important is Anirudh to Loki's films? 

32:17 - 34:27 - What were the various contributions of Anirudh to LEO? 

34:28 - 36:14 - How does Loki work with Anbariv to get the fight choreography on point in Leo? 

36:15 - 37:35 - Does Loki think that the stunts got a bit generic in certain scenes in the second half? 

37:36 - 39:24 - What was the most satisfying response Loki got post the release of Leo? What was his biggest takeaway? 

39:25 - 41:10 - Loki opens up on the LCU Routemap
 
41:11 - 43:23 - Loki signs off by talking about his next biggie,  Thalaivar 171

Join the Nakkalites Fzone team as they explore the challenges and joys of baby planning in a rural village. snippet.title: LEO - Thalapathy Vijay Speech | Success meet at Nehru stadium | Review
snippet.description:
#Leo 

"Join us as we celebrate the remarkable success of Thalapathy Vijay's blockbuster movie 'Leo' at the grand Success Meet, set to take place on November 1 at the iconic Nehru Stadium. It's an event that promises to be filled with excitement and fanfare, as we come together to honor the incredible achievements of this film. Be part of the buzz, as the star-studded cast and crew come together to share their insights and experiences from the making of this cinematic masterpiece. This is your chance to get up close and personal with the stars and immerse yourself in the magic of 'Leo'."

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 378
snippet.description:
രാം കുമാറിന് ഇത്തിരി ചുറ്റിക്കളി കൂടുന്നുണ്ട്. ദിയയും ഹൈമവതിയും ഈ കള്ളത്തരം പൊളിക്കാനുള്ള പ്ലാനിലാണ്. സഹായത്തിനായി ദിയ നീലുവിന്റെ അടുത്ത് എത്തിയിട്ടുണ്ട്. ഒപ്പം ലെച്ചുവും കുട്ടിപട്ടാളങ്ങളും ചേർന്നിട്ടുണ്ട്. വരാനിരിക്കുന്ന പൊല്ലാപ്പ് എന്താണേലും ചെറുതായിരിക്കില്ല. കാത്തിരുന്ന് കാണാം!!


Ram Kumar is doing something fishy. Diya and Haimavathi are planning to find out what he is hiding. Diya has approached Neelu for help, and Lechu and Kuttipattalams have joined the mission. Something big is coming. Let's see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'!"

snippet.title: Kiara Adani से लेकर Parineeti Chopra और Katrina Kaif तक... नई नवेली दुल्हनों ने यूं मनाया करवा चौथ
snippet.description:
Kiara Adani से लेकर Parineeti Chopra और Katrina Kaif तक... नई नवेली दुल्हनों ने यूं मनाया करवा चौथ

1 नवंबर को देशभर में करवा चौथ का त्यौहार धूम धाम से मनाया गया। बीती रात बॉलीवुड में भी चांद पर धरती पर उतर आया... हर साल की तरह इस साल भी बॉलीवुड की कई अभिनेत्रियों और स्टार वाइव्स ने अपने सजना के लिए व्रत रखा....और चांद के दीदार करने के बाद ही अपने व्रत को खोला...सोशल मीडिया भी बॉलीवुड हसीनाओं के करवा चौथ सेलिब्रेशन की तस्वीरों से भरा पड़ा है। जिनमें सबसे स्पेशल है बॉलीवुड की नई दुल्हनों की तस्वीरें

snippet.title: Emiway x Savlon Swasth India – HAATH DHONA COOL HAI #HandwashLegend ft. The Dharavi Dream Project
snippet.description:
This Iconic Hip-Hop move 👏🏼 is now the HANDWASHING Move!
Now after the hack, comes the track!

The track aims to make washing hands with Handwash or Soap cool in the minds of children, keeping them healthy and safe from various illnesses.

Let’s all wash our hands and become a #HandwashLegend.
___

ITC's Savlon Swasth India Mission - one of the largest school programmes of its kind, is committed to seeding hand hygiene habits in over 85 lakh school children, through continuous awareness and engagement activities.  
___

The Dharavi Dream Project After School of Hip-Hop is a non-profit organisation based in Mumbai. Through various educational programmes, mentorships and community engagement initiatives, it supports children living in Dharavi, Mumbai which today is known for its culturally vibrant hip-hop talent.

#HandwashingForAll #SavlonSwasthIndiaMission
___

Audio Credits:
Song :- HAATH DHONA COOL HAI 
Artist / Lyrics : EmiwayBantai
Prod by : Emiway Bantai 
Mix & mastered by :- Emiway bantai

बॉलीवुड की गॉर्जियस डिवा और बच्चन बहू ऐश्वर्या राय बच्चन पूरे 50 साल की हो गई हैं। बीते दिन, 1 नवंबर को जहां देश भर में ‘करवा चौथ' का त्यौहार मनाया गया। तो..वहीं, बुधवार को ही हमारी ब्यूटीफुल ऐश का 50th बर्थडे भी था। अब जब इतना खास दिन था..तो, भला इसका सेलिब्रेशन कैसे खास नहीं होता? तभी तो, अपनी ‘गोल्डन जुबली’ पर ऐश्वर्या ने कोई ग्रैंड पार्टी या जश्न नहीं..बल्कि, अपने पिता की याद में 1 करोड़ रूपये का दान किया और अपनी बेटी आराध्या बच्चन और मां बृंदा राय के साथ अपने खास दिन को सेलिब्रेट किया।#aishwaryaraibachchan #aaradhyabachchan #bollywood  #e24

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3917 | 1 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3917: Babita Ka Mushkil Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha gets worried about Babita's gift as she wishes to have a present related to the Moon. Jetha falls asleep while engrossed in his thoughts and he dreams about it. In his dream, Jetha and Babita have landed on the Moon through a rocket. Babita is extremely happy and she shows gratitude to Jetha for fulfilling her wish. Jetha's beautiful dream gets jeopardized when Sundar appears and offers him a glass of water. Watch the episode to find out what happens further!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3917, 1 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER
snippet.description:
Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER... I have to take a CHICKEN to beat the ender dragon. My friend has to stop me. Should be easy right?

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dream

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

This video is a different Minecraft challenge concept that we have never done before! It's similar to Minecraft Manhunt, in that I have to beat the game while George tries to hunt the CHICKEN, instead of me. The chicken heals over time like a player, and has 20 hearts.

It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftChallenge

2023  करवा चौथ व्रत कथा | करवा चौथ व्रत 2023 | Karwa Chauth Vrat Katha 2023 | Karwa Chauth Song 2023

करवा चौथ हिन्दुओं का एक प्रमुख त्योहार है। यह भारत के जम्मू[1], हिमाचल प्रदेश, पंजाब, उत्तर प्रदेश, हरियाणा, मध्य प्रदेश और राजस्थान में मनाया जाने वाला पर्व है। यह कार्तिक मास की कृष्ण पक्ष की चतुर्थी को मनाया जाता है। यह पर्व सौभाग्यवती (सुहागिन) स्त्रियाँ मनाती हैं। यह व्रत सवेरे सूर्योदय से पहले लगभग 4 बजे से आरंभ होकर रात में चंद्रमा दर्शन के उपरांत संपूर्ण होता है।

ग्रामीण स्त्रियों से लेकर आधुनिक महिलाओं तक सभी नारियाँ करवाचौथ का व्रत बडी़ श्रद्धा एवं उत्साह के साथ रखती हैं। शास्त्रों के अनुसार यह व्रत कार्तिक मास के कृष्णपक्ष की चन्द्रोदय व्यापिनी चतुर्थी के दिन करना चाहिए। पति की दीर्घायु एवं अखण्ड सौभाग्य की प्राप्ति के लिए इस दिन भालचन्द्र गणेश जी की अर्चना की जाती है। करवाचौथ में भी संकष्टीगणेश चतुर्थी के जैसे दिन भर उपवास रखकर रात में चन्द्रमा को अ‌र्घ्य देने के उपरांत ही भोजन करने का विधान है। वर्तमान समय में करवाचौथ व्रतोत्सव अधिकतर महिलाएं अपने परिवार में प्रचलित प्रथा के अनुसार ही मनाती हैं लेकिन अधिकतर स्त्रियां निराहार रहकर चन्द्रोदय की प्रतीक्षा करती हैं।

करवा चौथ हिन्दुओं का एक प्रमुख त्योहार है। यह भारत के जम्मू[1], हिमाचल प्रदेश, पंजाब, उत्तर प्रदेश, हरियाणा, मध्य प्रदेश और राजस्थान में मनाया जाने वाला पर्व है। यह कार्तिक मास की कृष्ण पक्ष की चतुर्थी को मनाया जाता है। यह पर्व सौभाग्यवती (सुहागिन) स्त्रियाँ मनाती हैं। यह व्रत सवेरे सूर्योदय से पहले लगभग 4 बजे से आरंभ होकर रात में चंद्रमा दर्शन के उपरांत संपूर्ण होता है।

ग्रामीण स्त्रियों से लेकर आधुनिक महिलाओं तक सभी नारियाँ करवाचौथ का व्रत बडी़ श्रद्धा एवं उत्साह के साथ रखती हैं। शास्त्रों के अनुसार यह व्रत कार्तिक मास के कृष्णपक्ष की चन्द्रोदय व्यापिनी चतुर्थी के दिन करना चाहिए। पति की दीर्घायु एवं अखण्ड सौभाग्य की प्राप्ति के लिए इस दिन भालचन्द्र गणेश जी की अर्चना की जाती है। करवाचौथ में भी संकष्टीगणेश चतुर्थी के जैसे दिन भर उपवास रखकर रात में चन्द्रमा को अ‌र्घ्य देने के उपरांत ही भोजन करने का विधान है। वर्तमान समय में करवाचौथ व्रतोत्सव अधिकतर महिलाएं अपने परिवार में प्रचलित प्रथा के अनुसार ही मनाती हैं लेकिन अधिकतर स्त्रियां निराहार रहकर चन्द्रोदय की प्रतीक्षा करती हैं।

snippet.description:

Episode 3916: The Perfect Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha apologizes to Babita for the present misunderstanding. Jetha also asks Babita to assist him in selecting an acceptable gift for his client, who is Bengali like her. Babita first hesitates, wondering how she could choose a present for someone she has never met. Later, she says that, in her opinion, sweets are a great way to win any Bengali's heart. Jetha expressly asks Babits' preference, and she responds that any Moon-related present would be her favorite. Jetha runs to Taarak for assistance. What is Jetha going to do now?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3916, 31 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Baylagaam Episode 23 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 1st November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

snippet.description:
Habra : চিতার বালিশে নোটের বান্ডিল! দাহ করতে গিয়ে তাড়া তাড়া নোট। চিতার আধপোড়া বালিশ থেকে উদ্ধার নোটের বান্ডিল। ভ্যান চালকের মৃত্যুতে চাঞ্চল্য ঘোজাডাঙায়।

#habra #habranews #habranewstoday #banglanews #news18bangla

Habra : চিতার বালিশে নোটের বান্ডিল! দাহ করতে গিয়ে তাড়া তাড়া নোট। চিতার আধপোড়া বালিশ থেকে উদ্ধার নোটের বান্ডিল। ভ্যান চালকের মৃত্যুতে চাঞ্চল্য ঘোজাডাঙায়।

#habra #habranews #habranewstoday #banglanews #news18bangla 

n18oc_south-bengal


News 18 Bangla is an exclusive news channel on YouTube which streams news related to West Bengal, Nation and the World. The channel also has contemporary topic based debate and subject special series which are interesting & informative. Our channel aims to update the viewers with the current news.

বাংলার প্রথম সারির খবরের চ্যানেল নিউজ18 বাংলা ৷ গত বেশ কয়েকবছর ধরে সাফল্যের সঙ্গে খবর পরিবশেন করে আসছে এই চ্যানেল ৷ ব্রেকিং নিউজ থেকে শুরু করে রাজনীতির খবর ৷ জেলা, ক্রাইম, বিনোদন, খেলা, ব্যবসা-বাণিজ্য, প্রাইম টাইম ডিবেট- সব খবর সবার আগে জানতে, দেখতে থাকুন News18 Bangla ৷ চ্যানেলের পাশাপাশি নিউজ18 বাংলার ওয়েবসাইট https://bengali.news18.com/-এ নজর রাখুন ৷
